{"tid":2478337,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"《福布斯》公佈全球首富 貝索斯連續第4年冧莊","createTime":"2021-04-07T03:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T03:47:59.000Z","uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c2570ed79048e91f25fa5436885700694e945bf8","tid":2478337,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"美國財經雜誌《福布斯》周二公佈2021年全球億萬富豪榜，由亞馬遜創辦人貝索斯（Jeff Bezos）以1,770億美元（1.38萬億港元）身家，連續第4年蟬聯全球首富。<br />\n<br />\n全球五大億萬富豪包括榜首的貝索斯，他連續第4年蟬聯榜首，今秋將辭任亞馬遜CEO。其次是去年排名第31位的Tesla行政總裁馬斯克（Elon Musk），其身家急增至1,510億美元（1.18萬億港元）；排第三的是LVMH董事長兼行政總裁阿諾特（Bernard Arnault）及家族，身家有1,500億美元（1.17萬億港元），至於微軟創辦人蓋茨及Facebook創辦人朱克伯格，就分別以1,240億美元（9,672億港元）及970億美元（7,566億港元）身家排名第四及第五。<br />\n<br />\n「股神」巴菲特五大不入，是1993年以來首次未打入富豪榜前五，不過他的身家仍比2020年高出285億美元（2,223億港元），達960億美元（7,488億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210406/YI4J5OCY7BBQJMWZXGFEWIMUNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210406%2FYI4J5OCY7BBQJMWZXGFEWIMUNY%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtHdT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=49bdf1c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210406%2FYI4J5OCY7BBQJMWZXGFEWIMUNY%2F&h=8341c4b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210406/YI4J5OCY7BBQJMWZXGFEWIMUNY/</a>"},{"pid":"d7db8ec6a42ae20e292119bd9eefacb07dbc63a3","tid":2478337,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"血汗工廠狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MollyJongFast/status/1375048872419061760?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMollyJongFast%2Fstatus%2F1375048872419061760%3Fs%3D20&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtHdT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=448fa702\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FM